channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: New Minor League Hockey Team in Athens, Georgia, Pays Tribute to B-52s with ‘Rock Lobsters’ Moniker
item.description: More than 8,000 people voted on new FPHL franchise's name; nod to one of the local band's best-known songs won by a margin of 565 votes

item.title: MLS Launches Latest Version of ‘Love Unites’ Pre-Match Tops in Time for Pride Month
item.description: Jerseys were designed in collaboration with Brazilian drag queen and pop singer Pabllo Vittar and will be worn prior to matches throughout June

item.description: Rory McIlroy was not in the mood to discuss his personal life while facing a pool of reporters at the PGA Championship on Wednesday ... sticking to sports as he fielded questions. TMZ Sports broke the story -- the 35-year-old golf superstar filed…

item.title: EA Sports’ College Football 25 Standard Edition Cover Leaks
item.description: Although it won't officially be revealed until Thursday morning, the Standard Edition cover for EA Sports' College Football 25 video game was leaked on social media on Wednesday morning.

item.title: Where Two Rivers Meet: Olympique Lyonnais Unveil 2024-25 Home Kit
item.description: Traditional red and blue stripes on the front of Lyon's 2024-25 kits said to be inspired by the city's two rivers, the Rhône and the Saône
